message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the sub-category for Sound and Music Computing, which is the most relevant sub-category for speech enhancement. Other likely sub-categories could include cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.SI (Signal Processing). These sub-categories are also relevant to speech enhancement as they involve machine learning, natural language processing, image and video processing, and signal processing, respectively.
